<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031768>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Lutosa morselli n. sp. female. A. Habitus in lateral view. B. Face. C. Head and pronotum in lateral view. D. Terminalia in axial and E. lateral views respectively. F. Subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031768/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031788>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Lutosa goeldiana female. A. Habitus in lateral and B. dorsal view. C. Face. D–E. Subgenital plate in ventral and axial views. (Photos: J. Hollier)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031788/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031792>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Lutosa paranaensis female. A. Habitus in lateral view. B. Face. C. Head and thorax in lateral view (see the absence of tympana). D. Terminalia in dorsal view. E. Subgenital plate. F. Ovipositor in lateral view. (Photos B. Garcete)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031774>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Lutosa quaresmai n. sp. female. A. Habitus in lateral and B. dorsal view. C. Face. D. Subgenital plate. E. Last tergites in axial view. F. Hind tibia apex in dorsal view. G. Ovipositor in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031774/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031776>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Lutosa marginalis female. A. Habitus in lateral view. B. Face. C. Head and thorax in lateral view. D. Terminalia in dorsal and E. lateral view respectively. F. Subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031776/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

